Predator:



Being captured and forced into these fights was not Predator's idea of fun.  
The bounty hunter leapt forward, the missiles impacting near him but not 
close enough, only sending shrapnel into his skidplate.  He cursed, raising 
his grenade launcher.

"I may not want to be part of this stupid IGL thingy, but that doesn't mean I 
won't splatter your insides against the walls!"
